            "<strong>Cost to outsource: $70/week</strong>",
            "<strong>His time's opportunity cost: $216/week</strong>",
            "(6 hours Ã— $36/hour)",
            "By doing chores himself, Marcus \"saved\" $70 but gave up $216 in potential earnings or high-value activities.",
